The Bible version I like the best is the Authorised King James Version,
as it is very accurate and brings out the best of the English language.

The script setup-linux-kjv.sh will download various versions of the
KJV-1900, also known as the Pure Cambridge Edition. See
http://www.bibleprotector.com/


List of KJV-1900 (PCE) Bibles:

https://duckduckgo.com/?q=Holman+KJV+Study+Bible --- Holman KJV Study Bible (Many versions)
ISBN-13: 9781434103819 --- The Holy Bible: King James Version, Pure Cambridge Edition (Paperback)
ISBN-13: 9781434104045 --- The Holy Bible: King James Version, Pure Cambridge Edition (Hardcover)
ISBN-13: 9781434104052 --- The Holy Bible: King James Version, Pure Cambridge Edition (Hardcover)
ISBN-13: 9780907861591 --- TBS Calfskin Family Bible

